detail_description: Fly into action with this Superman action figure. As the Man of Steel, Superman uses his superhuman abilities to protect Metropolis and fight for justice. Suitable for ages 6 and up.
Unleash the power of the Amazon warrior with this Wonder Woman action figure. Armed with her Lasso of Truth and indestructible bracelets, she fights for peace and justice. Suitable for ages 6 and up.
Gotham City needs its Dark Knight! Become Batman and protect the city from the villains with this action figure. Complete with Batarangs and a grappling hook. Suitable for ages 6 and up.
Race into action with The Flash action figure. With superhuman speed and lightning-fast reflexes, The Flash is the fastest man alive. Suitable for ages 6 and up.
Dive into adventure with this Aquaman action figure. As the King of Atlantis, Aquaman commands the power of the ocean and protects both land and sea. Suitable for ages 6 and up.
Swing into action with this Spider-Man action figure. Join the web-slinger on his heroic adventures and save the day. Suitable for ages 4 and up.
Smash your way into action with this Hulk action figure. Featuring incredible strength and durability, Hulk is ready to take on any challenge. Suitable for ages 4 and up.
Fight for freedom and justice with this Captain America action figure. Equipped with his shield, Captain America leads the Avengers in their battle against evil. Suitable for ages 5 and up.
Join the ranks of S.H.I.E.L.D. with this Black Widow action figure. Highly trained in combat and espionage, Black Widow is a formidable ally in the fight against evil. Suitable for ages 4 and up.
Harness the power of lightning with this Thor action figure. Thor, the God of Thunder, wields his mighty hammer Mjolnir to protect the realms from evil. Suitable for ages 6 and up.
I am Groot! Bring home the lovable and heroic Groot with this action figure. With his unique abilities and heart of gold, Groot is ready to save the galaxy. Suitable for ages 4 and up.

Get ready for some intergalactic action with this Rocket action figure. As a master marksman and expert tactician, Rocket is a valuable member of the Guardians of the Galaxy. Suitable for ages 6 and up.

Witness the might of the Mad Titan with this Thanos action figure. As the ultimate villain in the Marvel Universe, Thanos seeks to balance the universe with the power of the Infinity Stones. Suitable for ages 6 and up.
Enter the mystical realm with this Doctor Strange action figure. Master of the mystic arts, Doctor Strange protects the Earth from supernatural threats. Suitable for ages 6 and up.
Join the super-powered Parr family with this Mr. Incredible action figure. With super strength and invulnerability, Mr. Incredible is a true hero. Suitable for ages 6 and up.
Stretch your imagination with this Elastigirl action figure. As a superheroine with incredible flexibility, Elastigirl fights crime and protects her family. Suitable for ages 6 and up.
Unleash the power of force fields with this Violet action figure. As the shy yet formidable member of the Incredibles, Violet protects her family and fights evil. Suitable for ages 6 and up.
Speed into action with this Dash action figure. As the fastest member of the Incredibles, Dash uses his super speed to outmaneuver villains and save the day. Suitable for ages 6 and up.
Discover the unpredictable powers of Jack-Jack with this action figure. As the youngest member of the Incredibles, Jack-Jack showcases a range of incredible abilities. Suitable for ages 4 and up.
Embrace the dark side of superheroics with this Homelander action figure. As the twisted leader of The Seven, Homelander possesses immense power and a sinister agenda. Suitable for ages 16 and up.
Join the fight against corrupt superheroes with this Billy Butcher action figure. As the leader of The Boys, Billy is relentless in his pursuit of justice. Suitable for ages 16 and up.
Illuminate the darkness with this Starlight action figure. As a member of The Seven, Starlight possesses incredible light-based powers and fights for truth and justice. Suitable for ages 16 and up.
Unleash the power of the original superhero with this Soldier Boy action figure. As a legendary member of The Seven, Soldier Boy has a rich history of heroic exploits. Suitable for ages 16 and up.
Unmask the mystery of Black Noir with this action figure. As a silent and deadly member of The Seven, Black Noir strikes fear into the hearts of evildoers. Suitable for ages 16 and up.
Unleash the fury of Wolverine with this action figure. With his retractable adamantium claws and accelerated healing, Wolverine is an unstoppable force. Suitable for ages 6 and up.
Command the power of the elements with this Storm action figure. As a mutant with weather-manipulating abilities, Storm is a crucial member of the X-Men. Suitable for ages 6 and up.
Unleash optic blasts with this Cyclops action figure. As the leader of the X-Men, Cyclops possesses the ability to emit powerful energy beams from his eyes. Suitable for ages 6 and up.
Harness the power of the Phoenix with this Jean Grey action figure. As a powerful telepath and telekinetic, Jean Grey is a formidable member of the X-Men. Suitable for ages 6 and up.
Unleash the ferocity and intellect of Beast with this action figure. As a mutant with superhuman strength and agility, Beast is a valuable asset to the X-Men. Suitable for ages 6 and up.
Embrace the dark symbiote with this Venom action figure. Known for his menacing appearance and deadly abilities, Venom is a force to be reckoned with. Suitable for ages 14 and up.
Unleash the paranormal hero with this Hellboy action figure. As a half-demon with a powerful right hand, Hellboy battles supernatural threats. Suitable for ages 14 and up.

Harness the power of will with this Green Lantern action figure. As a member of the Green Lantern Corps, Green Lantern wields a ring that creates constructs from pure energy. Suitable for ages 6 and up.
Bring home the leader of the Ninja Turtles with this Leonardo action figure. Join him in his epic battles against Shredder and the Foot Clan. Suitable for ages 4 and up.
Unleash the intelligence and bo staff skills of Donatello with this action figure. Join him in fighting crime and protecting the city from evil. Suitable for ages 4 and up.
Join the fun-loving and pizza-obsessed Michelangelo on his adventures with this action figure. Cowabunga dude! Suitable for ages 4 and up.
Get ready for some sai-wielding action with Raphael. Join him in fighting crime and protecting the city from the forces of evil. Suitable for ages 4 and up.
